net.proteusframework.core.hibernate

Class PseudoHiLoSequenceGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.hibernate.PseudoHiLoSequenceGenerator

  • public class PseudoHiLoSequenceGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Implementation of the SequenceHiLoGenerator algorithm that does not use Hibernate. Used to generate new values for data conversions.

    Example in Groovy: 
     
   def sql = new Sql(_dataConfig.dataSource())
      PseudoHiLoSequenceGenerator generator = new PseudoHiLoSequenceGenerator({
         sql.firstRow($/SELECT nextVal('app.your_id_seq') AS newid/$).newid
      })
      Long generatedId = generator.generate()
    Author:
    Alan Holt (aholt@venturetech.net)
